sql: SELECT Freight_Metric_Tonnes, Fastest_Qualifying FROM airport_aircraft JOIN airport JOIN match JOIN aircraft ON aircraft.Aircraft_ID = match.Winning_Aircraft AND airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID = aircraft.Aircraft_ID AND airport.Airport_ID = airport_aircraft.Airport_ID WHERE International_Passengers BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Aircraft_Movements < 65 GROUP BY Fastest_Qualifying LIMIT 4

SELECT AVG(r.International_Passengers), r.Freight_Metric_Tonnes, r.Domestic_Passengers FROM airport AS r WHERE  r.International_Passengers <= 68 GROUP BY r.Domestic_Passengers HAVING MIN(r.Aircraft_Movements) = 87 ORDER BY r.Freight_Metric_Tonnes ASC

SELECT Pilot_Id, ID FROM airport_aircraft JOIN pilot JOIN match JOIN aircraft ON match.Winning_Pilot = pilot.Pilot_Id AND aircraft.Aircraft_ID = match.Winning_Aircraft AND airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID = aircraft.Aircraft_ID WHERE  Airport_ID <= 84 ORDER BY ID DESC
SELECT Location FROM match WHERE  Round <= 87 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM aircraft WHERE match.Round = Aircraft_ID)
SELECT Country FROM match JOIN aircraft ON aircraft.Aircraft_ID = match.Winning_Aircraft WHERE  Round < 8 ORDER BY Country DESC
SELECT Max_Gross_Weight, Country FROM pilot JOIN match JOIN aircraft ON match.Winning_Pilot = pilot.Pilot_Id AND aircraft.Aircraft_ID = match.Winning_Aircraft WHERE  Pilot_Id <= 58

SELECT Round FROM airport_aircraft JOIN pilot JOIN match JOIN aircraft ON match.Winning_Pilot = pilot.Pilot_Id AND aircraft.Aircraft_ID = match.Winning_Aircraft AND airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID = aircraft.Aircraft_ID WHERE  airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID <= 22 LIMIT 4
SELECT MAX(ID), Airport_Name FROM airport_aircraft JOIN airport ON airport.Airport_ID = airport_aircraft.Airport_ID WHERE  Domestic_Passengers <= 45
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT match.Location), h.Round FROM match AS h JOIN match ON match.Round = h.Round WHERE match.Round BETWEEN 1 AND 10

SELECT Round, Country, Winning_Aircraft FROM match WHERE Round BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM aircraft AS g WHERE  g.Aircraft_ID <= 58 AND match.Round = g.Aircraft_ID) GROUP BY Winning_Aircraft
SELECT AVG(Age), COUNT(Pilot_Id), Name FROM pilot WHERE Pilot_Id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM match AS j WHERE pilot.Pilot_Id = j.Winning_Pilot LIMIT 10) LIMIT 2
SELECT Name FROM pilot WHERE  Pilot_Id <= 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM match AS b WHERE  b.Round <= 100 AND pilot.Pilot_Id = b.Winning_Pilot) ORDER BY Name ASC
SELECT Round, Winning_Pilot FROM match JOIN aircraft ON aircraft.Aircraft_ID = match.Winning_Aircraft WHERE  Round > 71 LIMIT 4
SELECT z.Max_disk_Loading FROM aircraft AS z WHERE z.Aircraft_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  z.Aircraft_ID > 63
SELECT Aircraft_ID, ID FROM airport_aircraft WHERE  Aircraft_ID = 32 GROUP BY ID ORDER BY ID DESC LIMIT 2

SELECT airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID, airport_aircraft.Airport_ID FROM airport_aircraft JOIN airport JOIN aircraft ON airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID = aircraft.Aircraft_ID AND airport.Airport_ID = airport_aircraft.Airport_ID
SELECT AVG(Round), COUNT(DISTINCT Description) FROM pilot JOIN match JOIN aircraft ON match.Winning_Pilot = pilot.Pilot_Id AND aircraft.Aircraft_ID = match.Winning_Aircraft WHERE  Pilot_Id = 100

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Max_disk_Loading), airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID, Total_disk_area FROM airport_aircraft JOIN match JOIN aircraft ON aircraft.Aircraft_ID = match.Winning_Aircraft AND airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID = aircraft.Aircraft_ID WHERE  ID < 40 GROUP BY Total_disk_area HAVING MIN(airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID) > 84
SELECT Date FROM match WHERE Round BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Round < 21

SELECT Max_Gross_Weight, Winning_Aircraft FROM airport_aircraft JOIN pilot JOIN match JOIN aircraft ON match.Winning_Pilot = pilot.Pilot_Id AND aircraft.Aircraft_ID = match.Winning_Aircraft AND airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID = aircraft.Aircraft_ID WHERE  Age != 26
SELECT a.Airport_Name FROM airport AS a WHERE Airport_ID IN (SELECT Airport_ID FROM airport AS l WHERE  l.Airport_ID <= 77)
SELECT MAX(Pilot_Id), Pilot_Id FROM pilot WHERE  Age < 47
SELECT Aircraft_ID FROM aircraft WHERE  Aircraft_ID > 94 ORDER BY Aircraft_ID DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT MIN(ID), ID FROM airport_aircraft JOIN airport ON airport.Airport_ID = airport_aircraft.Airport_ID WHERE  Aircraft_Movements <= 44
SELECT m.Age, m.Name FROM pilot AS m WHERE Age >= (SELECT AVG(Age) FROM pilot WHERE  Pilot_Id != 0 LIMIT 2) LIMIT 8
SELECT MIN(Pilot_Id), Name FROM pilot
SELECT Domestic_Passengers FROM airport WHERE  Freight_Metric_Tonnes != 21 LIMIT 4
SELECT Age FROM pilot WHERE  Pilot_Id = 13 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM match WHERE Round BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Round <= 91 AND pilot.Pilot_Id = Winning_Pilot) ORDER BY Age DESC

SELECT AVG(airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID), Airport_ID FROM airport_aircraft JOIN aircraft ON airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID = aircraft.Aircraft_ID WHERE  aircraft.Aircraft_ID > 88 ORDER BY Airport_ID ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT Max_disk_Loading, Fastest_Qualifying FROM airport_aircraft JOIN pilot JOIN match JOIN aircraft ON match.Winning_Pilot = pilot.Pilot_Id AND aircraft.Aircraft_ID = match.Winning_Aircraft AND airport_aircraft.Aircraft_ID = aircraft.Aircraft_ID WHERE  aircraft.Aircraft_ID < 3 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM pilot WHERE  Age <= 72 AND match.Round = Pilot_Id) GROUP BY Fastest_Qualifying HAVING MAX(Age) < 19
